ۚ"],"translation":"(yaitu) Tuhan (pemelihara) langit, bumi, dan apa yang ada di antara keduanya, Yang Maha Pengasih. Mereka tidak memiliki (hak) berbicara dengan-Nya.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":78,"arabic":"النّبأ","latin":"An-Naba'","transliteration":"An-Naba'","translation":"Berita","num_ayah":40,"page":582,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5710,"surah_id":78,"ayah":38,"page":583,"quarter_hizb":59,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"يَوْمَ يَقُوْمُ الرُّوْحُ وَالْمَلٰۤىِٕكَةُ صَفًّاۙ  لَّا يَتَكَلَّمُوْنَ اِلَّا مَنْ اَذِنَ لَهُ الرَّحْمٰنُ وَقَالَ صَوَابًا","kitabah":"يَوْمَ يَقُوْمُ الرُّوْحُ وَالْمَلٰۤىِٕكَةُ صَفًّاۙ  لَّا يَتَكَلَّمُوْنَ اِلَّا مَنْ اَذِنَ لَهُ الرَّحْمٰنُ وَقَالَ صَوَابًا","latin":"Yauma yaqūmur-rūḥu wal-malā'ikatu ṣaffā(n), lā yatakallamūna illā man ażina lahur-raḥmānu wa qāla ṣawābā(n).","arabic_words":["يَوْمَ","يَقُوْمُ","الرُّوْحُ","وَالْمَلٰۤىِٕكَةُ","صَفًّاۙ","لَّا","يَتَكَلَّمُوْنَ","اِلَّا","مَنْ","اَذِنَ","لَهُ","الرَّحْمٰنُ","وَقَالَ","صَوَابًا"],"translation":"Pada hari ketika Rūḥ743) dan malaikat berdiri bersaf-saf. Mereka tidak berbicara, kecuali yang diizinkan oleh Tuhan Yang Maha Pengasih dan dia mengatakan yang benar.","footnotes":"743) Para ahli tafsir berbeda pendapat mengenai maksud rūḥ pada ayat ini. Ada yang memahaminya sebagai Jibril, tentara Allah, atau malaikat yang diserahi tugas mengurus arwah dan sejenisnya.","updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":78,"arabic":"النّبأ","latin":"An-Naba'","transliteration":"An-Naba'","translation":"Berita","num_ayah":40,"page":582,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5711,"surah_id":78,"ayah":39,"page":583,"quarter_hizb":59,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"ذٰلِكَ الْيَوْمُ الْحَقُّۚ فَمَنْ شَاۤءَ اتَّخَذَ اِلٰى رَبِّهٖ مَاٰبًا","kitabah":"ذٰلِكَ الْيَوْمُ الْحَقُّۚ فَمَنْ شَاۤءَ اتَّخَذَ اِلٰى رَبِّهٖ مَاٰبًا","latin":"Żālikal-yaumul-ḥaqq(u), faman syā'attakhaża ilā rabbihī ma'ābā(n).","arabic_words":["ذٰلِكَ","الْيَوْمُ","الْحَقُّۚ","فَمَنْ","شَاۤءَ","اتَّخَذَ","اِلٰى","رَبِّهٖ","مَاٰبًا"],"translation":"Itulah hari yang hak (pasti terjadi). Siapa yang menghendaki (keselamatan) niscaya menempuh jalan kembali kepada Tuhannya (dengan beramal saleh).","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":78,"arabic":"النّبأ","latin":"An-Naba'","transliteration":"An-Naba'","translation":"Berita","num_ayah":40,"page":582,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5712,"surah_id":78,"ayah":40,"page":583,"quarter_hizb":59,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"arabic":"اِنَّآ اَنْذَرْنٰكُمْ عَذَابًا قَرِيْبًا ەۙ يَّوْمَ يَنْظُرُ الْمَرْءُ مَا قَدَّمَتْ يَدَاهُ وَيَقُوْلُ الْكٰفِرُ يٰلَيْتَنِيْ كُنْتُ تُرٰبًا ࣖ","kitabah":"اِنَّآ اَنْذَرْنٰكُمْ عَذَابًا قَرِيْبًا ەۙ يَّوْمَ يَنْظُرُ الْمَرْءُ مَا قَدَّمَتْ يَدَاهُ وَيَقُوْلُ الْكٰفِرُ يٰلَيْتَنِيْ كُنْتُ تُرٰبًا ࣖ","latin":"Innā anżarnākum ‘ażāban qarībā(n), yauma yanẓurul-mar'u mā qaddamat yadāhu wa yaqūlul-kāfiru yā laitanī kuntu turābā(n).","arabic_words":["اِنَّآ","اَنْذَرْنٰكُمْ","عَذَابًا","قَرِيْبًا","ەۙ","يَّوْمَ","يَنْظُرُ","الْمَرْءُ","مَا","قَدَّمَتْ","يَدَاهُ","وَيَقُوْلُ","الْكٰفِرُ","يٰلَيْتَنِيْ","كُنْتُ","تُرٰبًاࣖ"],"translation":"Sesungguhnya Kami telah memperingatkan kamu akan azab yang dekat pada hari (ketika) manusia melihat apa yang telah diperbuat oleh kedua tangannya dan orang kafir berkata, “Oh, seandainya saja aku menjadi tanah.”","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":78,"arabic":"النّبأ","latin":"An-Naba'","transliteration":"An-Naba'","translation":"Berita","num_ayah":40,"page":582,"location":"Makkiyah"}}]}